,"tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-knowledge-al-ilm","tag-light-al-nur-noor","tag-manners-adab","tag-al-quran","tag-recitation-al-tilawah","tag-reward-al-ajr","tag-surah-al-kahf","tag-virtue-al-fadail","tag-worship-al-ibadah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-128","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":3987,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/03\/dajjal-ten-verses-kahf\/","url_meta":{"origin":3976,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dajjal: Verses of Al-Kahf protect from False Messiah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever memorizes ten verses from the beginning of Surat al-Kahf\u00a0will be immune to the False Messiah.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \"From the last ten verses of Surat al-Kahf.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 809 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3984,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/03\/sakina-surat-al-kahf\/","url_meta":{"origin":3976,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sakinah: Tranquility descends with Quran recitation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara\u2019 ibn \u2018Azib reported: A man was reciting Surat al-Kahf, and an animal became unsettled in his barn. As he looked, there was a mist or a cloud overshadowing him. The man mentioned that to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \"Keep reciting, O you,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14036,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/07\/ibn-masud-quran-old-treasures\/","url_meta":{"origin":3976,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Quran: Middle chapters are my old treasures","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Yazid reported: Ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said about Surat Bani Isra'il, Al-Kahf, Maryam, Ta Ha, and Al-Anbiya', \"They were among the first chapters I learned and they are my old treasures.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4431 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u064a\u0632\u064a\u062f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19591,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/26\/al-ala-ghashiyah-jumuah-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":3976,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Surat al-A&#8217;la and al-Ghashiyah in Eid, Friday prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Num\u2019an ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would recite in the two Eid prayers and in the Friday prayer the chapters, \u201cGlorify the name of your Lord the Most High,\u201d (87:1) and, \u201cHas there come to you the news of the overwhelming?\u201d (88:1).\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35124,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/01\/allah-gives-no-weight\/","url_meta":{"origin":3976,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fame: Allah gives no weight to worldly status","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, a prominent and obese man will be brought on the Day of Resurrection who does not weigh as much as a gnat's wing to Allah. Recite the verse: Thus, We will not give them any\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31792,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/shield-fire-dhikr-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":3976,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Your shield from Hellfire is remembrance of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTake up your shields.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is the enemy present?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cNo, rather your shields from the Hellfire are to declare the glory of Allah, the praise of Allah, there\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_con